
Request type: GET

Search Medicine by name:

URI : http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/name/<name>				[replace <name> with medicine name]
eg: http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/name/Crocin

Search Medicine by Generic name:

URI : http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/genericName/<GenericName>				[replace <GenericName> with generic name]
eg: http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/genericName/paracetmol

Search Medicine by Category name:

URI : http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/categoryName/<CategoryName>				[replace <CategoryName> with Category name]
eg: http://localhost:8081/restapi/medicineInfo/categoryName/antibiotic